caption:
Carlsberg is the Official Beer of UEFA National Team Football!

Carlsberg and UEFA go way back, with a history that began with UEFA EURO 1988, and we’re over the moon to be partnering once again to provide greater access to the beautiful game. 

After all, Carlsberg and football make a great team ⚽💪. We can’t wait to welcome you along for the ride and show how you can get involved. Is this the beginning of an exciting new chapter together? Probably.
